chapter.verse:
E meere ɓe mawnintayam;
E ɓe ekkitina dooka yimɓe
bo to am ɗum ƴiwoyi.’

O wi'i, “Onon on kokkaama faamu sirru Laamu Allah, ammaa woɓɓe sey e misaalu ɗu'um, ngam
‘e ɓe ndaara, ammaa ɓe ngi'ataa;
e ɓe nana, ammaa ɓe paamataa.’ ”

Mi hollay fii kulniiɗum e dow;
nder duuniyaaru boo mi waɗay alaamaaji kulniiɗi,
waato ƴiiƴam e hiite e curka ɓaleha.

Nden Icaaya metii e sembe ɓernde wi'ii Allah wi'ii,
“Ɓen ɗon ɓe ɗaɓɓitataayam ɓe keɓiiyam;
mi wanginii hoore am to yimɓe ɓe ƴamaayi no ɓe keɓirtayam.”

Nden Dawda wi'ii,
“Allah waɗa humto maɓɓe wartanaɓe tarkowol
ɓe njana nder maggol, ɓe njara torra no haananiɓe;

Neɗɗo am aadiliijo o jooɗoto laawol hoolaakiyam;
ammaa to o yaatirii gaɗa,
mi nanataa belɗum maako.”
